{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2925165, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个收入占比是什么意思呀？", "timestamp": 1636772162, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925166, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这个表也很好地诠释了二八定律，在高收入人群内，最高的20%的人拿走了80%的收入", "timestamp": 1636772175, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925168, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2925165, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 这一组的收入总和，除以五组的收入总和", "timestamp": 1636772221, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925175, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是谁一年赚45个亿？？？？？啥企业啊这是", "timestamp": 1636772252, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925181, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2925175, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 45亿不多吧，比如阿里巴巴2021财年净利润1719.85亿元", "timestamp": 1636772301, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925205, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "最低收入组平均年收入17w，这是纯扯淡吧", "timestamp": 1636772639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925218, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "70万人月入两万是家庭人均，是指这样的家庭有70w人", "timestamp": 1636772771, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925225, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "但是超过24w有1844万人，感觉在扯淡", "timestamp": 1636772815, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925229, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2925225, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 中国的贫富差距超出你的想象了吧", "timestamp": 1636772861, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925259, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2925205, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 这是把高收入人群里又分成了五组", "timestamp": 1636773215, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925424, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "这数据明显伪造吧。每三百人里就有一个年入700万？cz生活在大城市还没遇到过这么有钱的", "timestamp": 1636774864, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2925605, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2925424, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 你解读的不对，平均700万，最小值肯定小于700万，中位数也肯定小于700万。每300里就有一个的应该是年入256万以上。", "timestamp": 1636776180, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2926260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2925181, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 阿里巴巴是企业，个人45亿还不多？？？啊这", "timestamp": 1636781123, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2926931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2926260, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 1000亿净利润，假设拿出10%来分红，那么只要持股5%的股东就可以收入50亿了", "timestamp": 1636787700, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2926939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 556269, "reply_to": 2926260, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 我的意思不是不多，而是全国收入最高的那个人收入45亿并不是什么离谱的事情，不能证明这个数据是编的", "timestamp": 1636787768, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 518, "w": 1080}, "likenum": 12, "pid": 556269, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "“全国月入2万以上只有70万人”应该是讹传。\n\n全国年收入超过24万的至少有1844万人。\n\n来源是北师大中国收入分配研究院的《中国居民收入分配年度报告（2019）》表16-3。", "timestamp": 1636772089, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1636787766, "url": "rz/rzymdkp4ot4iqbiizaovqldptdsdrdiy.jpeg", "vote": {}}}